Class SnomedDescription

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.core.domain.BaseComponent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IComponent, Serializable

    public final class SnomedDescription
extends SnomedCoreComponent
    Represents a SNOMED CT Description.

    Information about the inactivation reason can also be retrieved from this object if applicable.
